text: ยง 11-423 Sales and foreclosures of tax liens. Notwithstanding any of the provisions of this chapter the city may continue to sell tax liens, transfer the same to purchasers and become the purchaser at such sales of tax liens in the manner provided by this title.

chapter.text: TAX LIEN FORECLOSURE BY ACTION IN REM
